<item>
            <title>[SYNAPSE-938] [PTT] Http Proxy not working with PassThroughHttpSender</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SYNAPSE-938</link>
                <project id="12310201" key="SYNAPSE">Synapse</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;In Nhttp transport we can define http proxy parameters as follows to send messages through a http proxy.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&amp;lt;transportSender name=&quot;http&quot;  class=&quot;org.apache.synapse.transport.nhttp.HttpCoreNIOSender&quot;&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
        &amp;lt;parameter name=&quot;non-blocking&quot; locked=&quot;false&quot;&amp;gt;true&amp;lt;/parameter&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
        &amp;lt;parameter name=&quot;warnOnHTTP500&quot; locked=&quot;false&quot;&amp;gt;*&amp;lt;/parameter&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
        &amp;lt;parameter name=&quot;http.proxyHost&quot; locked=&quot;false&quot;&amp;gt;proxy.synapse.org&amp;lt;/parameter&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
        &amp;lt;parameter name=&quot;http.proxyPort&quot; locked=&quot;false&quot;&amp;gt;3128&amp;lt;/parameter&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
        &amp;lt;parameter name=&quot;http.nonProxyHosts&quot; locked=&quot;false&quot;&amp;gt;.&lt;b&gt;.foo.synapse.org|.&lt;/b&gt;.bar.synapse.org&amp;lt;/parameter&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
    &amp;lt;/transportSender&amp;gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;But in PassThroughHttpSender this configuration does not work.&lt;/p&gt;

</description>
